1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:01,510
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,510 --> 00:00:02,540
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:02,540 --> 00:00:03,580
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:04,940 --> 00:00:06,210
(Episode 82)

5
00:00:06,680 --> 00:00:08,310
I knew it.

6
00:00:09,780 --> 00:00:11,980
Kim Dan Hui isn't going
to the board meeting.

7
00:00:23,030 --> 00:00:26,200
That's right. Giving up early
is a great idea.

8
00:00:27,900 --> 00:00:30,670
If it's so great,
then you should give up too.

9
00:00:31,270 --> 00:00:34,140
Because Dan Hui's already heading
to the board meeting.

10
00:00:34,510 --> 00:00:35,510
What?

11
00:00:51,490 --> 00:00:52,620
Hurry and go inside.

12
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:54,390
Thank you for your help.

13
00:00:54,690 --> 00:00:56,830
But how did you know
there was an issue...

14
00:00:56,830 --> 00:00:58,160
with the emergency board meeting?

15
00:00:58,660 --> 00:01:02,500
We can talk about that later.
Hurry and go inside.

16
00:01:02,970 --> 00:01:04,370
Yes, thank you.

17
00:01:13,910 --> 00:01:17,120
Kim Dan Hui will attend
the board meeting.

18
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:35,130
The recording wasn't fabricated.
It's completely real.

19
00:01:35,930 --> 00:01:36,940
Park Tae Ho...

20
00:01:37,940 --> 00:01:40,910
is the man who murdered my sister.

21
00:01:54,550 --> 00:01:55,850
It's all a lie.

22
00:01:57,420 --> 00:02:00,790
I'm not Kim Myung Hui.
I'm Kim Dan Hui.

23
00:02:01,390 --> 00:02:05,560
And just as the recording states,
Park Tae Ho took my sister from me.

24
00:02:06,430 --> 00:02:07,700
Deceived by Park Tae Ho,

25
00:02:08,070 --> 00:02:11,440
he has made a mockery of my life
for the past 30 years.

26
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:14,040
Park Tae Ho...

27
00:02:14,940 --> 00:02:18,340
is unfit to be the chairman
of Adele Group.

28
00:02:23,780 --> 00:02:27,650
No, it's all lies. It's a trap.

29
00:02:28,190 --> 00:02:31,120
These are lies meant to drag me down
from my position as chairman.

30
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:36,960
There's no proof anywhere
that I murdered anyone.

31
00:02:38,630 --> 00:02:39,630
Yes, that's right.

32
00:02:42,200 --> 00:02:45,640
When we aren't even sure
if the recording is authentic,

33
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:47,810
are you going to believe someone...

34
00:02:49,970 --> 00:02:52,740
who has lived under a false identity
for the last 30 years,

35
00:02:53,980 --> 00:02:56,610
or the chairman
who built Adele Group?

36
00:02:57,850 --> 00:02:59,250
I'll let you be the judge of that.

37
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,150
As the chairman's son,

38
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,590
I believe my father is innocent.

39
00:03:26,480 --> 00:03:28,650
When the heck
did Kim Dan Hui get away?

40
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:31,250
I need to get into the meeting
and testify.

41
00:03:32,350 --> 00:03:34,550
I must side with Park Tae Ho
and say Kim Dan Hui is lying.

42
00:03:34,620 --> 00:03:36,090
It's the only way
to stop his dismissal.

43
00:03:38,290 --> 00:03:40,660
I think the board meeting
has already started.

44
00:03:42,260 --> 00:03:43,260
Not so fast.

45
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:46,430
You can't go into the board meeting.

46
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:49,170
Wait. What are you doing here?

47
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:51,870
Don't tell me...

48
00:03:52,570 --> 00:03:54,610
Are you really scheming
with that witch, Kim Dan Hui?

49
00:03:54,810 --> 00:03:57,510
Oh please, "scheming" is such
an unrefined word.

50
00:03:57,710 --> 00:04:00,280
There's a much better word for it.
"Collaboration."

51
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:02,180
Collaboration, my foot.

52
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:05,750
I had a bad feeling
about you and Chloe from the start.

53
00:04:05,850 --> 00:04:07,350
I knew my instincts were right.

54
00:04:07,550 --> 00:04:09,990
I guess you wouldn't know
what good taste is.

55
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:13,020
You actually followed me
all the way here?

56
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:16,790
You're trying to get in
Dan Hui's way. I have to stop you.

57
00:04:17,200 --> 00:04:20,930
Every time you tormented her,
I wanted to tear you to pieces.

58
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:24,940
Today, we're finally settling...

59
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:26,640
this 30-year grudge.

60
00:04:28,340 --> 00:04:31,140
Kim Dan Hui, Chloe,
and the whole lot of you.

61
00:04:31,410 --> 00:04:33,040
You're all in this lie together.

62
00:04:33,880 --> 00:04:36,050
Are your true, dark colors
finally showing?

63
00:04:37,650 --> 00:04:40,320
When it comes to having
a black heart, you take the cake.

64
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:42,390
Get lost. Now.

65
00:04:43,020 --> 00:04:44,490
And stay out of Dan Hui's way.

66
00:04:45,460 --> 00:04:46,690
Why you....

67
00:04:47,130 --> 00:04:48,160
Easy now.

68
00:04:48,760 --> 00:04:50,230
- What...
- Don't.

69
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:55,600
- You can't go in.
- We have to get in.

70
00:04:58,300 --> 00:05:03,010
Fine. The police investigation
will reveal the truth.

71
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,280
The meeting ends here.

72
00:05:06,410 --> 00:05:09,280
Since the board meeting has begun,
we must proceed to a vote.

73
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,120
What?

74
00:05:13,050 --> 00:05:15,320
Go right ahead then.

75
00:05:16,950 --> 00:05:21,060
You know how I've operated
throughout my life.

76
00:05:23,190 --> 00:05:24,700
Anyone who betrays me...

77
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,100
will pay.

78
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:30,670
Everyone, don't let
Park Tae Ho's threats sway you.

79
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:33,870
The recording isn't fake. It's real.

80
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:42,610
(The bloodstain is a 99.99 percent match
to Park Tae Ho.)

81
00:05:44,250 --> 00:05:46,750
What are these DNA analysis results?

82
00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:50,860
What?

83
00:06:07,970 --> 00:06:11,840
From the evidence left
at the crime scene 30 years ago,

84
00:06:12,910 --> 00:06:14,980
a trace of Park Tae Ho's blood
was found.

85
00:06:19,720 --> 00:06:20,750
Wait!

86
00:06:21,650 --> 00:06:25,390
Hey. What are you all doing?
That's all fake too.

87
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:29,430
Just ignore that and cast your vote.

88
00:06:30,030 --> 00:06:31,030
Right now!

89
00:06:37,570 --> 00:06:38,570
Move aside.

90
00:06:39,170 --> 00:06:41,110
I need to attend
the board meeting too.

91
00:06:41,370 --> 00:06:44,780
You can't leave
without the chairman's permission.

92
00:06:45,380 --> 00:06:46,540
Manager Kang!

93
00:06:49,980 --> 00:06:52,250
I'll now announce
the results of the vote.

94
00:06:53,220 --> 00:06:56,150
The motion to dismiss
Chairman Park Tae Ho...

95
00:07:02,430 --> 00:07:03,630
has passed.

96
00:07:23,110 --> 00:07:24,980
What is this nonsense?

97
00:07:24,980 --> 00:07:26,950
Who dares to try and take me down?

98
00:07:27,390 --> 00:07:31,520
I am the Adele Group,
and the Adele Group is me.

99
00:07:32,960 --> 00:07:34,860
No one can take down...

100
00:07:35,860 --> 00:07:37,930
Park Tae Ho.

101
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:42,830
This concludes the emergency...

102
00:07:43,570 --> 00:07:44,800
board meeting.

103
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:46,570
Well then,

104
00:07:46,770 --> 00:07:48,410
at the next regular board meeting,

105
00:07:48,410 --> 00:07:50,240
let's discuss electing
the next chairman.

106
00:07:50,510 --> 00:07:53,510
In accordance with
the majority shareholder's opinion,

107
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:55,550
I'd like to recommend Kim Dan Hui.

108
00:07:57,180 --> 00:07:59,450
What? What are you talking about?

109
00:07:59,750 --> 00:08:01,950
Who gave you the right
to recommend Kim Dan Hui?

110
00:08:02,390 --> 00:08:06,790
I'll prove my innocence
by the next board meeting.

111
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:11,460
So be ready to cancel my dismissal.

112
00:08:19,300 --> 00:08:20,740
Hey!

113
00:08:21,240 --> 00:08:25,440
All of you.
You'll regret dismissing me.

114
00:08:28,280 --> 00:08:29,810
I'm innocent!

115
00:08:30,620 --> 00:08:32,920
I won't be taken down like this.

116
00:08:52,070 --> 00:08:53,340
What happened?

117
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:55,640
Was the chairman really dismissed?

118
00:09:07,220 --> 00:09:08,490
Kim Dan Hui.

119
00:09:09,250 --> 00:09:11,660
- How dare you...
- Park Tae Ho.

120
00:09:12,590 --> 00:09:16,130
Your days of using Adele's power
as you please are officially over.

121
00:09:17,230 --> 00:09:20,500
You won't be able to hide the fact
that you're a murderer either.

122
00:09:20,930 --> 00:09:24,640
All the other sins you've committed,
one by one,

123
00:09:24,970 --> 00:09:26,570
will all come to light.

124
00:09:27,370 --> 00:09:29,870
Just because I've been
removed as chairman,

125
00:09:30,270 --> 00:09:31,780
do you think I'm finished?

126
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:35,210
Do you have any idea
how I got to this position?

127
00:09:36,480 --> 00:09:39,120
At the next board meeting,

128
00:09:39,780 --> 00:09:41,790
I'll take my position
as chairman right back.

129
00:09:43,990 --> 00:09:46,020
It won't be that easy.

130
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,160
You...

131
00:09:50,160 --> 00:09:52,500
The evidence that
you murdered someone...

132
00:09:52,560 --> 00:09:53,970
seems pretty conclusive.

133
00:09:54,130 --> 00:09:55,970
For breaching
the joint development agreement,

134
00:09:55,970 --> 00:09:58,040
my company, JKL Partners,

135
00:09:58,100 --> 00:10:00,270
will be filing a lawsuit
to claim damages.

136
00:10:01,010 --> 00:10:05,910
Do you really think a murderer
who's being sued for damages...

137
00:10:06,780 --> 00:10:08,750
has a chance
of becoming chairman again?

138
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:09,910
What?

139
00:10:13,950 --> 00:10:16,790
I knew it.
You didn't lose your memory.

140
00:10:16,890 --> 00:10:19,720
You actually faked amnesia
just to team up with Kim Dan Hui...

141
00:10:19,960 --> 00:10:22,230
and stab me in the back.

142
00:10:26,530 --> 00:10:27,530
Yes.

143
00:10:27,830 --> 00:10:29,070
That's right.

144
00:10:29,070 --> 00:10:33,540
I haven't forgotten
what happened at the warehouse.

145
00:10:37,010 --> 00:10:38,440
Just as I thought.

146
00:10:38,810 --> 00:10:42,910
I suppose I can report
the warehouse incident too,

147
00:10:44,180 --> 00:10:46,850
along with all the accomplices.

148
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:54,890
You two better be ready.

149
00:10:54,930 --> 00:10:59,230
You're going to pay a heavy price
for deceiving me.

150
00:11:01,830 --> 00:11:03,170
Let's go, Father.

151
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:05,840
This isn't over yet,

152
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:08,570
so there's no need
to cause more trouble here.

153
00:11:34,370 --> 00:11:35,800
Park Tae Ho.

154
00:11:36,230 --> 00:11:37,640
We brought him down.

155
00:11:38,200 --> 00:11:40,670
Yes, and this is just the beginning.

156
00:11:40,770 --> 00:11:43,710
Right. We'll keep pressing him
with the lawsuit...

157
00:11:43,770 --> 00:11:45,240
and the warehouse incident.

158
00:11:45,580 --> 00:11:48,480
Soon, he'll pay
for everything he did,

159
00:11:49,450 --> 00:11:51,020
including my father's accident
seven years ago.

160
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:53,580
Yes. He definitely should.

161
00:11:55,050 --> 00:11:56,250
But...

162
00:11:56,890 --> 00:11:58,890
what happened with Hyun Jun?

163
00:11:59,360 --> 00:12:01,960
Why is he suddenly
taking Park Tae Ho's side?

164
00:12:03,590 --> 00:12:06,960
I think I caused
a bit of a misunderstanding.

165
00:12:09,230 --> 00:12:11,270
- Come on. It's almost over.
- Honey.

166
00:12:11,670 --> 00:12:12,670
Hyun Jun.

167
00:12:13,770 --> 00:12:15,210
What happened at the board meeting?

168
00:12:15,210 --> 00:12:16,670
You kept
your chairman position, right?

169
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:18,480
Why you...

170
00:12:20,850 --> 00:12:23,210
Wait. Don't tell me you were fired.

171
00:12:23,210 --> 00:12:24,350
The motion for dismissal...

172
00:12:25,750 --> 00:12:26,950
was passed.

173
00:12:28,020 --> 00:12:29,020
What?

174
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:32,760
So in the end...

175
00:12:34,290 --> 00:12:35,960
This isn't over.

176
00:12:38,630 --> 00:12:39,630
Honey.

177
00:13:00,420 --> 00:13:04,490
- Hyun Jun sided with Park Tae Ho.
- Yes.

178
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:09,090
Jin Ju said it seems
he misunderstood something,

179
00:13:09,460 --> 00:13:11,130
but it still sits wrong with me.

180
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:13,860
He'll come around
once the misunderstanding is cleared up.

181
00:13:14,630 --> 00:13:18,940
Let's just focus on the fact
that Park Tae Ho was dismissed.

182
00:13:19,500 --> 00:13:22,370
Our Dan Hui and Jin Ju
finally did it.

183
00:13:22,710 --> 00:13:23,710
That's right.

184
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:26,210
After years of hard work,

185
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:28,410
they finally got some payback
on Park Tae Ho.

186
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:31,650
I know. This is wonderful.

187
00:13:32,950 --> 00:13:34,050
Dan Hui...

188
00:13:35,250 --> 00:13:39,160
To think she was deceived
for 30 years...

189
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:43,060
Hey, why are you crying
on a wonderful day like this?

190
00:13:44,300 --> 00:13:45,760
I'm happy...

191
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:47,730
I'm so happy, but...

192
00:13:48,370 --> 00:13:51,570
When I think of those 30 years...

193
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:54,170
Hey, don't cry. Come on, it's okay.

194
00:13:54,310 --> 00:13:57,810
Here, look. There, there.

195
00:14:03,110 --> 00:14:04,280
No, wait...

196
00:14:05,980 --> 00:14:07,050
Oh my.

197
00:14:13,890 --> 00:14:15,090
He was dismissed?

198
00:14:17,560 --> 00:14:21,030
Yes, I'll go see the chairman
right away.

199
00:14:21,700 --> 00:14:23,800
Did the dismissal motion pass?

200
00:14:32,010 --> 00:14:34,310
- Min Jun.
- Mother.

201
00:14:35,250 --> 00:14:36,950
The dismissal motion passed, right?

202
00:14:37,010 --> 00:14:40,850
That's right. Park Tae Ho
was kicked out as chairman.

203
00:14:43,250 --> 00:14:44,560
That's a relief.

204
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:48,160
Wait. Where's Jin Ju?

205
00:14:48,230 --> 00:14:52,160
Don't worry. She's probably meeting
with Ms. Choi now.

206
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:04,410
With the chairman kicked out,

207
00:15:05,510 --> 00:15:07,680
if Chloe reports
the warehouse incident,

208
00:15:08,150 --> 00:15:09,510
what will happen to me?

209
00:15:10,750 --> 00:15:13,250
If Park Min Jun reveals the incident
from seven years ago,

210
00:15:13,780 --> 00:15:15,590
will I be unable
to stop that either?

211
00:15:18,720 --> 00:15:20,160
Probably.

212
00:15:28,800 --> 00:15:32,570
You had a lot of fun, didn't you?

213
00:15:33,600 --> 00:15:34,610
What?

214
00:15:34,670 --> 00:15:37,410
You took advantage
of Park Min Jun's memory loss...

215
00:15:37,410 --> 00:15:39,040
to pretend to be his girlfriend,

216
00:15:39,210 --> 00:15:42,910
and then you blackmailed Hyun Jun
with his secret.

217
00:15:43,150 --> 00:15:45,220
Riding the coattails
of Oh Jung Ran and Park Tae Ho,

218
00:15:45,220 --> 00:15:46,480
you acted like you were somebody.

219
00:15:47,950 --> 00:15:52,690
It hasn't been easy putting up
with you running wild so brazenly.

220
00:15:53,090 --> 00:15:54,090
What?

221
00:15:54,930 --> 00:15:56,460
Park Hyun Jun's secret?

222
00:15:58,260 --> 00:15:59,760
Don't tell me you know about it too.

223
00:16:03,070 --> 00:16:04,800
So don't even think...

224
00:16:05,500 --> 00:16:08,670
about using his secret
as leverage again.

225
00:16:09,170 --> 00:16:12,540
You'd better take
my warning seriously.

226
00:16:12,540 --> 00:16:13,740
Your warning?

227
00:16:14,380 --> 00:16:17,650
Things are about to get
a lot harder for you.

228
00:16:18,580 --> 00:16:21,520
You'll regret the day
you betrayed me,

229
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:25,660
and all the wrong you've done
will come back to destroy you.

230
00:16:28,190 --> 00:16:31,130
No. I've done nothing wrong.

231
00:16:31,500 --> 00:16:32,600
What happened at the warehouse...

232
00:16:32,660 --> 00:16:34,500
was your own fault
for trying to use me.

233
00:16:34,870 --> 00:16:37,800
It was your fault for trying
to kill Chairman Park.

234
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:43,140
Yes, the fact that you still
have no remorse...

235
00:16:43,210 --> 00:16:44,680
is a great relief.

236
00:16:45,740 --> 00:16:46,880
Then,

237
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:49,010
let's see you endure what's coming.

238
00:16:57,790 --> 00:16:59,690
I can't go down like this.

239
00:17:00,560 --> 00:17:02,260
I have to survive somehow,

240
00:17:02,860 --> 00:17:05,200
even if it means clinging
to the chairman or Hyun Jun.

241
00:17:11,840 --> 00:17:13,470
- Manager Kang.
- Yes, sir.

242
00:17:13,470 --> 00:17:16,270
Get Detective Yun in here right now.

243
00:17:16,940 --> 00:17:18,640
You mean Deputy Chief Yun?

244
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:20,980
Right. I'll use that jerk...

245
00:17:21,350 --> 00:17:24,680
to take care of Kim Dan Hui,
so bring him here.

246
00:17:24,750 --> 00:17:26,020
Yes, I understand.

247
00:17:33,790 --> 00:17:34,790
What was that?

248
00:17:35,090 --> 00:17:37,230
What did you just order
Manager Kang to do?

249
00:17:37,630 --> 00:17:39,260
It's none of your business.

250
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:42,500
Oh Jung Ran, you're the president
of the bio division,

251
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:45,270
so fire that traitor Park Min Jun
right now.

252
00:17:45,700 --> 00:17:47,440
Kick him out of the company.

253
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:49,340
That's not what's important
right now.

254
00:17:49,610 --> 00:17:52,980
First, we need to decide what to do
about the chairman's position.

255
00:17:52,980 --> 00:17:55,280
What? We?

256
00:17:55,810 --> 00:17:57,350
That's right.

257
00:17:57,350 --> 00:18:00,680
You watched him ditch Chloe
and take your side.

258
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:08,730
I tried to kill Chloe
at the warehouse.

259
00:18:08,790 --> 00:18:11,660
The guy who acted like Chloe
was his whole world...

260
00:18:11,660 --> 00:18:13,160
took my side?

261
00:18:14,870 --> 00:18:16,430
Real or not,

262
00:18:17,630 --> 00:18:19,140
I'm not buying it.

263
00:18:21,410 --> 00:18:22,410
Right.

264
00:18:23,640 --> 00:18:26,180
Normally, I couldn't have
forgiven you, Father.

265
00:18:26,180 --> 00:18:29,950
But then I found out
Chloe was just using me.

266
00:18:30,910 --> 00:18:33,120
I decided I couldn't let her
get her way.

267
00:18:34,150 --> 00:18:35,150
That's right.

268
00:18:35,150 --> 00:18:39,260
Chloe pretended to have amnesia
and used our Hyun Jun.

269
00:18:39,590 --> 00:18:42,590
Hyun Jun has come to his senses now.

270
00:18:43,060 --> 00:18:45,560
Neither of us can afford
to lose like this, Father.

271
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:47,360
At the next board meeting,

272
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:49,200
they'll discuss
electing the next chairman.

273
00:18:49,770 --> 00:18:51,140
We need a plan.

274
00:18:51,770 --> 00:18:52,770
A plan?

275
00:18:53,440 --> 00:18:54,810
In the current situation,

276
00:18:54,870 --> 00:18:57,540
it'll be difficult
for you to return, Father.

277
00:18:58,310 --> 00:19:01,510
Back me to take your place.

278
00:19:03,210 --> 00:19:05,150
I'll step up as the next chairman.

279
00:19:08,650 --> 00:19:09,650
Hyun Jun.

280
00:19:10,190 --> 00:19:11,520
Never forget...

281
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:14,020
that you still have your son...

282
00:19:14,630 --> 00:19:15,830
by your side, Father.

283
00:19:17,460 --> 00:19:21,200
He's right.
Just trust our Hyun Jun this once.

284
00:19:24,500 --> 00:19:25,500
Trust you?

285
00:19:28,110 --> 00:19:29,110
The two of you?

286
00:19:38,120 --> 00:19:40,150
All right. Drink up, everyone.

287
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:43,220
Man, just knowing
that scumbag Park Tae Ho is out...

288
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:46,160
makes it feel like a 30-year burden
has finally been lifted.

289
00:19:46,620 --> 00:19:48,560
But then I think
of all those who suffered,

290
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:50,260
and I just get choked up.

291
00:19:51,700 --> 00:19:53,960
I know things
were tough today, Mother.

292
00:19:53,960 --> 00:19:54,970
Not at all.

293
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:57,770
You and Jin Ju went through more.

294
00:19:57,770 --> 00:19:59,300
Preparing for the board meeting...

295
00:19:59,370 --> 00:20:01,310
and even getting
the additional evidence.

296
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:03,240
You did well.

297
00:20:03,570 --> 00:20:04,640
Not at all.

298
00:20:04,640 --> 00:20:07,340
You coming to the board meeting
made a huge difference.

299
00:20:08,180 --> 00:20:11,050
You said Butler Ok got you out
of the basement, right?

300
00:20:11,250 --> 00:20:14,690
How did she know
something went wrong at the meeting?

301
00:20:14,750 --> 00:20:15,750
Beats me.

302
00:20:16,150 --> 00:20:17,250
Things were so hectic...

303
00:20:17,320 --> 00:20:19,420
that there was no time to talk
about the details.

304
00:20:20,020 --> 00:20:23,160
She always helps me out
whenever I'm in a pinch,

305
00:20:23,660 --> 00:20:25,360
but I don't know how she finds out.

306
00:20:25,930 --> 00:20:27,460
Yoon Jung, what do you think...

307
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:28,900
Have some more.

308
00:20:34,100 --> 00:20:36,540
Hold up. What's with you two?

309
00:20:37,110 --> 00:20:38,910
I can feel a shift in the air.

310
00:20:38,980 --> 00:20:41,380
What? What about us?

311
00:20:41,380 --> 00:20:43,180
Us?

312
00:20:44,280 --> 00:20:46,520
That's right. "Us."

313
00:20:46,520 --> 00:20:47,680
As of today, we...

314
00:20:47,680 --> 00:20:50,490
Starting today,
we have to work even harder.

315
00:20:50,750 --> 00:20:52,620
Chairman Park Tae Ho isn't the type
to just sit back,

316
00:20:52,620 --> 00:20:54,490
even though he was forced out.

317
00:20:54,490 --> 00:20:56,930
We have our work cut out for us.

318
00:21:01,230 --> 00:21:04,640
Yes, of course. That's right.

319
00:21:04,970 --> 00:21:09,240
We might have forced him out,
but we can't let our guard down.

320
00:21:09,270 --> 00:21:11,840
They'll discuss the next chairman
at the next board meeting,

321
00:21:12,140 --> 00:21:14,010
and he'll absolutely try
to reclaim his position right away.

322
00:21:14,080 --> 00:21:15,550
I'll try to get
the Temi Bio documentary done...

323
00:21:15,610 --> 00:21:16,610
as fast as possible.

324
00:21:17,210 --> 00:21:19,380
If the incident
from seven years ago comes to light,

325
00:21:19,380 --> 00:21:21,620
it'll be even harder for him
to be reinstated as chairman.

326
00:21:21,690 --> 00:21:25,190
But there's still a lot of time
before the board meeting.

327
00:21:25,460 --> 00:21:28,060
He could plot something
in the meantime.

328
00:21:28,130 --> 00:21:29,390
We have to be prepared.

329
00:21:29,630 --> 00:21:32,130
Then why don't we
win over public opinion...

330
00:21:32,130 --> 00:21:34,060
before the documentary airs?

331
00:21:34,500 --> 00:21:37,170
Public interest is high thanks to
Park Tae Ho's recording.

332
00:21:37,470 --> 00:21:41,640
We can hold a press conference
to formally expose his crimes.

333
00:21:42,340 --> 00:21:45,740
It's a chance for you to stand
before the world as Kim Dan Hui.

334
00:21:46,840 --> 00:21:50,110
Yes, and it'll play well to reveal
that you were nominated...

335
00:21:50,110 --> 00:21:51,520
to be the next chairman.

336
00:21:52,250 --> 00:21:54,450
Yes, that's a great idea.

337
00:21:54,850 --> 00:21:57,990
Reporters have been calling
from all over anyway.

338
00:21:59,260 --> 00:22:01,490
Everyone's curious to hear
your side of the story,

339
00:22:01,490 --> 00:22:02,660
so let's do it.

340
00:22:03,060 --> 00:22:05,660
All right, let's do it.

341
00:22:16,040 --> 00:22:18,780
For a man whose 30-year-old crime
was exposed...

342
00:22:18,780 --> 00:22:20,580
and who was forced out as chairman,

343
00:22:21,110 --> 00:22:22,810
you seem awfully relaxed.

344
00:22:23,680 --> 00:22:26,050
Just because they took
my chairman's nameplate,

345
00:22:26,350 --> 00:22:28,450
do you think this is the end of me?

346
00:22:29,090 --> 00:22:33,360
- I'm still the owner of Adele.
- So?

347
00:22:34,390 --> 00:22:36,690
After threatening me
into keeping my mouth shut,

348
00:22:36,760 --> 00:22:38,400
why did you call for me?

349
00:22:40,630 --> 00:22:42,600
Rather than hiring someone new,

350
00:22:43,770 --> 00:22:46,840
it's better to use someone
I already know.

351
00:22:48,970 --> 00:22:52,340
I'm not the same Detective Yun
I used to be.

352
00:22:52,740 --> 00:22:55,880
I'm not a tool for you to use
as you please.

353
00:22:56,050 --> 00:22:57,350
That's your response...

354
00:22:57,350 --> 00:22:59,380
when a 30-year-old incident
has just resurfaced?

355
00:22:59,750 --> 00:23:03,520
If Kim Dan Hui keeps exposing
what happened 30 years ago,

356
00:23:03,620 --> 00:23:05,820
do you think I'll be the only one
who goes down?

357
00:23:06,860 --> 00:23:10,230
Everything you did back then
will come to light too.

358
00:23:10,390 --> 00:23:12,900
So you're determined
to drag me down with you?

359
00:23:16,570 --> 00:23:17,970
Look here.

360
00:23:19,270 --> 00:23:20,400
I...

361
00:23:20,800 --> 00:23:23,140
will make sure you are...

362
00:23:23,870 --> 00:23:25,080
paid generously.

363
00:23:27,980 --> 00:23:31,750
So what is it you want me to do?

364
00:23:32,150 --> 00:23:34,990
Don't tell me you want me
to kill Kim Dan Hui.

365
00:23:35,050 --> 00:23:38,160
If that's what you want,
I will absolutely not do it.

366
00:23:39,090 --> 00:23:41,290
With that recording
spread everywhere,

367
00:23:41,360 --> 00:23:44,760
if Kim Dan Hui dies,
you'd be the prime suspect.

368
00:23:44,930 --> 00:23:47,900
The whole country is watching
this case,

369
00:23:48,300 --> 00:23:50,170
so my hands are tied.

370
00:23:52,270 --> 00:23:55,070
Do you think
I haven't thought of that?

371
00:23:57,040 --> 00:23:58,440
Even if we're going
to kill Kim Dan Hui,

372
00:23:59,610 --> 00:24:02,050
we need to do it differently.

373
00:24:02,750 --> 00:24:04,250
Differently?

374
00:24:10,190 --> 00:24:13,520
What could he be plotting
with Detective Yun?

375
00:24:15,260 --> 00:24:16,390
Does he plan to handle this...

376
00:24:16,390 --> 00:24:18,830
and reclaim
the chairmanship himself?

377
00:24:19,560 --> 00:24:22,330
- It seems he won't hand it to me.
- What?

378
00:24:24,900 --> 00:24:27,500
Then we'll have to change our plans.

379
00:24:27,740 --> 00:24:30,440
Mom, we can't miss this chance.

380
00:24:30,440 --> 00:24:32,140
You need to contact
the board immediately...

381
00:24:32,440 --> 00:24:35,010
and do whatever it takes
to block Father's return.

382
00:24:36,850 --> 00:24:37,850
I will.

383
00:24:42,520 --> 00:24:44,420
What?
Why are you looking at me like that?

384
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:49,060
Well, I'm glad to see you
wanting this for yourself,

385
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:52,630
but it's really not like you.

386
00:24:53,930 --> 00:24:55,230
You're the one who told me...

387
00:24:55,870 --> 00:24:57,930
that it's dangerous and pointless
to live your life...

388
00:24:57,930 --> 00:24:59,740
relying on other people.

389
00:25:00,940 --> 00:25:04,010
I've decided
not to trust anyone anymore.

390
00:25:04,640 --> 00:25:07,110
I'll become
Park Tae Ho's perfect son...

391
00:25:08,980 --> 00:25:10,580
and claim the chairmanship of Adele.

392
00:25:25,700 --> 00:25:26,830
Just...

393
00:25:28,800 --> 00:25:30,470
be yourself.

394
00:25:33,170 --> 00:25:35,310
It doesn't matter whose son you are.

395
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:37,940
Just be you, Hyun Jun.

396
00:25:40,110 --> 00:25:42,080
That's all you need to do.

397
00:25:45,650 --> 00:25:47,250
(Park Min Jun)

398
00:26:08,410 --> 00:26:10,340
Do you have time
to be calling me out here like this?

399
00:26:11,140 --> 00:26:14,310
Your mother... Oh, wait.
That's not right.

400
00:26:15,150 --> 00:26:16,650
She's your aunt, isn't she?

401
00:26:18,620 --> 00:26:20,820
Shouldn't you be sticking
by your aunt's side,

402
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:22,920
plotting how to steal
the chairman's seat,

403
00:26:23,020 --> 00:26:25,960
figuring out
how to use and deceive people?

404
00:26:27,120 --> 00:26:28,490
Isn't that
what you should be planning?

405
00:26:39,100 --> 00:26:43,870
You know everything
our father did to my mother and me.

406
00:26:44,440 --> 00:26:46,240
How can you say something like that?

407
00:26:46,580 --> 00:26:50,050
You say you love Jin Ju,
so how could you betray her?

408
00:26:50,150 --> 00:26:51,880
You and Baek Jin Ju...

409
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:55,620
betrayed me first.

410
00:26:56,550 --> 00:26:58,860
- What?
- You both knew my secret...

411
00:26:58,860 --> 00:26:59,960
but played dumb.

412
00:27:00,790 --> 00:27:01,930
I bet it was fun.

413
00:27:02,860 --> 00:27:05,700
Knowing I'm not
Chairman Park Tae Ho's son...

414
00:27:05,700 --> 00:27:09,570
and have no chance
of inheriting Adele Group,

415
00:27:10,770 --> 00:27:11,970
you pushed me out of the way...

416
00:27:14,070 --> 00:27:15,540
and teamed up again.

417
00:27:16,170 --> 00:27:18,710
- The circumstances were...
- The two of you!

418
00:27:20,410 --> 00:27:22,310
You pitied me and looked down on me,

419
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:24,880
and you trampled all over my pride.

420
00:27:27,620 --> 00:27:31,020
And yet, you only care
about your own pain, don't you?

421
00:27:31,620 --> 00:27:34,460
What about you?
You claim to love Jin Ju,

422
00:27:34,820 --> 00:27:37,090
but you still put yourself
before her.

423
00:27:37,860 --> 00:27:39,900
You were so caught up
in your secret being exposed...

424
00:27:40,430 --> 00:27:41,930
that you interfered
with Jin Ju's plans.

425
00:27:44,170 --> 00:27:46,200
Before this gets any messier,

426
00:27:46,700 --> 00:27:49,270
go meet Jin Ju and talk to her.

427
00:27:52,610 --> 00:27:55,150
Stop acting so high and mighty
and telling me what to do.

428
00:27:58,650 --> 00:28:00,480
Hey, Park Hyun Jun.

429
00:28:01,180 --> 00:28:02,190
Park Hyun Jun!

430
00:28:07,790 --> 00:28:10,660
Yes, I'll find a venue
for the press conference.

431
00:28:10,960 --> 00:28:13,560
James, please keep an eye
on Park Tae Ho's movements.

432
00:28:14,200 --> 00:28:16,300
I'm worried he's going to retaliate.

433
00:28:18,130 --> 00:28:19,140
Okay.

434
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:29,350
Because I'm not Park Tae Ho's son.

435
00:28:29,980 --> 00:28:31,980
Because I'm useless to you now!

436
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:36,150
(Park Hyun Jun)

437
00:28:48,730 --> 00:28:49,730
This misunderstanding...

438
00:28:50,570 --> 00:28:52,740
Where do I even begin
to clear this up?

439
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:58,140
(Chloe)

440
00:29:36,750 --> 00:29:37,750
No way.

441
00:29:38,280 --> 00:29:40,750
Dan Hui, you look amazing today.

442
00:29:41,250 --> 00:29:42,950
She's right. You look incredible.

443
00:29:43,950 --> 00:29:46,060
- Thank you.
- You must be nervous.

444
00:29:47,120 --> 00:29:49,390
I'm exposing Park Tae Ho's crimes.

445
00:29:49,730 --> 00:29:50,960
I can't afford to be nervous.

446
00:29:52,100 --> 00:29:53,100
Park Tae Ho.

447
00:29:53,630 --> 00:29:56,400
No matter how much he insists
they are lies, in the end,

448
00:29:57,500 --> 00:29:59,540
he'll end up a murderer
despised by all.

449
00:29:59,970 --> 00:30:02,840
Right. Once the Temi Bio documentary
is released,

450
00:30:03,240 --> 00:30:06,710
suspicions that he killed my father
will also grow.

451
00:30:07,710 --> 00:30:09,880
Then a reinvestigation
will be unavoidable.

452
00:30:10,310 --> 00:30:13,020
Yes, that's exactly
what will happen.

453
00:30:18,760 --> 00:30:20,360
(Exposing Chairman Park Tae Ho
as a Murderer...)

454
00:30:20,360 --> 00:30:21,960
(and Revealing
Kim Dan Hui's Identity)

455
00:30:23,830 --> 00:30:26,260
- What's going on?
- It's...

456
00:30:26,360 --> 00:30:27,400
- It's Kim Dan Hui.
- She's here.

457
00:30:27,460 --> 00:30:28,460
It's Kim Dan Hui!

458
00:30:42,680 --> 00:30:45,050
(Exposing Chairman Park Tae Ho
as a Murderer...)

459
00:30:45,050 --> 00:30:47,350
(and Revealing
Kim Dan Hui's Identity)

460
00:30:47,550 --> 00:30:48,590
Hello, everyone.

461
00:30:49,950 --> 00:30:50,950
My name is Kim Dan Hui.

462
00:30:51,850 --> 00:30:53,920
I stand before you today
not as Kim Myung Hui,

463
00:30:54,960 --> 00:30:56,530
but as Kim Dan Hui.

464
00:30:56,590 --> 00:30:57,590
What? What's going on?

465
00:30:57,660 --> 00:30:59,560
As you may have heard
from the released recording,

466
00:31:00,060 --> 00:31:01,200
thirty years ago,

467
00:31:02,470 --> 00:31:04,270
Adele Group's
Chairman Park Tae Ho...

468
00:31:06,370 --> 00:31:07,370
murdered my sister,

469
00:31:08,910 --> 00:31:11,110
- Kim Myung Hui.
- It wasn't me!

470
00:31:12,240 --> 00:31:13,310
Look, it's Park Tae Ho.

471
00:31:14,210 --> 00:31:15,280
It's Chairman Park Tae Ho.

472
00:31:16,610 --> 00:31:18,050
(Exposing Chairman Park Tae Ho
as a Murderer...)

473
00:31:25,390 --> 00:31:28,490
I am not a murderer.

474
00:31:29,090 --> 00:31:30,230
I am the victim.

475
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:33,560
I fell for Kim Dan Hui's scheme...

476
00:31:33,830 --> 00:31:37,130
and have been deceived
for the past 30 years.

477
00:31:39,370 --> 00:31:43,710
For 30 years, Kim Dan Hui
pretended to be Kim Myung Hui...

478
00:31:44,240 --> 00:31:45,940
and deceived me.

479
00:31:50,410 --> 00:31:51,410
Park Tae Ho.

480
00:31:52,380 --> 00:31:53,850
What are you talking about?

481
00:31:54,980 --> 00:31:58,020
I did not kill Kim Myung Hui.

482
00:31:59,320 --> 00:32:00,860
The one who killed Kim Myung Hui...

483
00:32:01,460 --> 00:32:04,960
was Kim Dan Hui, who wanted
to steal her twin sister's life.

484
00:32:11,970 --> 00:32:12,970
It was...

485
00:32:14,600 --> 00:32:15,910
that woman right there.

486
00:32:15,910 --> 00:32:17,170
Kim Dan Hui is the killer?

487
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:20,240
- Really? What's going on?
- Is Kim Dan Hui the murderer?

488
00:32:49,040 --> 00:32:52,080
(Pearl in Red)

489
00:32:52,210 --> 00:32:54,540
- Still, you built...
- It's Kim Dan Hui. You murderer!

490
00:32:54,610 --> 00:32:56,810
a certain kinship
after 30 years of closeness.

491
00:32:57,050 --> 00:32:59,920
She was literally just
an empty shell of Kim Myung Hui.

492
00:33:00,620 --> 00:33:01,850
That's all she was.

493
00:33:02,190 --> 00:33:03,190
To get reinstated as chairman.

494
00:33:03,190 --> 00:33:05,390
You framed me for murder
just for that?

495
00:33:05,590 --> 00:33:07,620
How dare you exploit
my sister's death like that?

496
00:33:07,620 --> 00:33:09,290
Kim Dan Hui, you!

497
00:33:09,790 --> 00:33:11,760
I can take you insulting me,

498
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:14,260
but I won't tolerate you
insulting my sister,

499
00:33:14,260 --> 00:33:15,470
who died at your hands.

500
00:33:16,600 --> 00:33:18,170
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
